                                    <div class="margin-bottom-5">
        <h3>General Perspectives on Knowledge Management: Fostering a Research Agenda</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="margin-bottom-10">
            <a href="/contributors/195">Grover, Varun</a> and     <a href="/contributors/439">Davenport, Thomas H</a>    </div>

<p>ABSTRACT: We trace in pragmatic terms some of what we know about knowledge, information technology, knowledge management practice and research, and provide two complementary frameworks that highlight potential opportunities for building a research agenda in this area. The papers in this special issue are then discussed.</p>

    <strong>Key words and phrases: </strong>
